name: when the rooster crows at night - indonesian myths
description:
a myth about what happens when a rooster crows from dusk until dawn.

When the rooster crows at dusk, it is a sign that an angel is approaching your house

when the rooster crows at midnight, it is a sign that there will be a disgrace that will unfold in society

When the rooster crows at dawn, it is believed to bring fertility and glory
